可以写得偏“跨团队协作、推动问题解决、提升测试效率”这种方向，适合测试工程师年终总结。
版本1（正式简洁）
Worked closely with cross-functional teams to align testing scope, troubleshoot critical issues, and improve delivery quality across multiple projects.
Collaborated with developers and infrastructure teams to identify potential risks early and provide optimization suggestions for system stability and performance.
Supported end-to-end testing activities by coordinating PT/RT execution, dependency checks, and issue tracking to ensure smooth project delivery.
版本2（突出主动性）
Actively collaborated with multiple teams during testing and incident handling, helping drive root cause analysis and improve troubleshooting efficiency.
Coordinated with stakeholders to validate expected behaviors, identify hidden defects, and reduce potential production risks through comprehensive testing coverage.
Contributed to automation framework improvements that streamlined testing workflows and enhanced team collaboration efficiency.
版本3（偏“携手合作”主题）
Fostered strong collaboration across testing, development, and operations teams to ensure efficient communication and high-quality delivery outcomes.
Partnered with different teams to optimize testing processes, improve incident response workflows, and enhance overall testing effectiveness.
Worked together with team members to continuously improve automation capabilities, reporting quality, and testing reliability.